				\begin{document}$$\text{Moisture} \; \text{content }\left({\%}\right)=\frac{Initial \; weight \; of \; the \; sample-final \; weight \; of \; the \; sample}{Initial \; weight \; of \; the \;sample}*100$$\end{document}
Moisture removed (Mr) from the biomass product was calculated using the following equations,Moistureremoved=mpMi-Mf100-Mf)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
